{"tid":1221991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢返part time經理比左張冇名嘅八達通我","createTime":"2019-06-14T10:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T10:50:30.000Z","uid":235880,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cc3abaa0353f807502d4a3cae38023982db20000","tid":1221991,"uid":235880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Rt6m9v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Rt6m9v.png&h=39c66b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n八達通「示意圖」<br />\n今日發夢見到返工嘅時候經理走過黎比張卡我<br />\n同我講睇到年青人嘅努力 要小心安全 呢到攞去啦<br />\n需要嘅呢到有晒 攞去搭車郊遊買野食防曬去野餐啦<br />\n個刻無神論嘅我就好似見到耶穌咁 好撚感動<br />\n知你發夢會上連登 想係到同你講多聲多謝<br />\n無錯有好多人有家庭負擔或者其他原因出唔到黎<br />\n但係都有好多有心人係佢地能力範圍內支持緊我地<br />\n希望同大家分享我夢見到嘅野可以比到正能量你地<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 繼續發夢<br />\n唔好相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ccd7c013098726ce9c80a9faaa26434377c0cd2","tid":1221991,"uid":235880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:36:03.000Z","msg":"唔小心開錯台添<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c660d5cf4714d36a53dee0f4f230cc880d1c4e92","tid":1221991,"uid":32380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"屌 成日 見到呢啲故事都眼濕濕仆街"},{"pid":"9fa8fe32fe0c5632cc569dc5dce14a700e517bbe","tid":1221991,"uid":235880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c660d5cf4714d36a53dee0f4f230cc880d1c4e92","tid":1221991,"uid":32380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"屌 成日 見到呢啲故事都眼濕濕仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"其實香港仲有希望 唔好再拖啦<br />\n自己香港自己救"}]}